pages.title: Coastal Salamander
pages.text: The coastal giant salamander ($(o)Dicamptodon tenebrosus$()) is a species of salamander in the family Dicamptodontidae ($(o)Pacific giant salamanders).$(br2)It is endemic to the Pacific Northwest of North America.
